    <ConstantCategory name="JSS_EX_CORE_SCHEMA" id="22afd28c-0fdd-430b-b9e6-019421edd369">
        <text>This category will contain all exception code constants, in the format
of "JSS_EX_nnnnn", where the "nnnnn" is a unique five-digit integer.

Note that alll Package schemas should have their own constant category
for excepton, but the category's name must begin with "JSS_EX_".</text>
    </ConstantCategory>
