    <ConstantCategory name="JSS_SORTER" id="2093ad6b-e260-4071-8b03-6e3893e60ce2">
        <text>___________________________________________________________________________

              P R O P R I E T A R Y   N O T I C E

This software, in whole and in every part, is proprietary to Jade Software
Corporation Limited at Christchurch, New Zealand and is not to be
reproduced, used or disclosed except upon prior written permission of Jade
Software Corporation Limited.

  COPYRIGHT © JADE SOFTWARE CORPORATION LIMITED 2002 - ALL RIGHTS RESERVED
____________________________________________________________________________

This category contains BaseSchema Exception Message codes.  The following
is a list of the code value ranges.  These exceptions will be raised with
the CnEcBaseException class.

BaseSchema Applications
=======================
01000 - 01199	BaseBackApp
01200 - 01399	BaseMethodGenerator
01400 - 01599	BaseSchemaMonitor
01600 - 01799	BaseWebTest
01800 - 01999	HCSadmin
02000 - 02199	HCSconfigure
02200 - 02399	HCSsetupWizard
02400 - 02599	IniEditor
02600 - 02799	JDBrowser
02800 - 02999	XMLUtility

BaseSchema Components
=====================
10000 - 11999	CnEcAgent
12000 - 13999	CnEcBaseEntity (general)
14000 - 15999	CnEcDataValue
16000 - 16999	CnEcLincSystemEntities
17000 - 18999	CnEcReportEntity
19000 - 19999	CnEcSerialInterface
20000 - 20999	CnEcSortEntity
21000 - 21999	CnEcXML
22000 - 23999	CnEcHtmlEntity

JADE Entities
=============
70000 - 71999	Application class
72000 - 73999	Collection classes
74000 - 75999	Connection classes
76000 - 77999	Control classes
78000 - 78999	Exception class
79000 - 79999	FileNode classes
80000 - 81999	Form classes
82000 - 82999	Global class
83000 - 84999	Primitive classes
85000 - 85999	Printer classes
86000 - 87999	SchemaEntity classes
88000 - 88999	System class
89000 - 89999	WebSession class</text>
    </ConstantCategory>
